00:08:57.310 --> 00:08:58.310
Yeah, that happens.

00:08:58.310 --> 00:08:58.910
ALAN: Or age into it.

00:08:58.910 --> 00:09:01.010
CHRISTY ALTOMARE: Or age
into it like in my case.

