JOHN BOLTON: You don't?

00:16:38.195 --> 00:16:38.610
CHRISTY ALTOMARE: You do?

00:16:38.610 --> 00:16:39.220
Oh I've tripped.

00:16:39.220 --> 00:16:39.520
JOHN BOLTON: I've trip on yours.

