I don't even know
what I'm saying.

00:16:41.730 --> 00:16:42.230
Yes.

00:16:42.230 --> 00:16:43.450
It happens.

00:16:43.450 --> 00:16:44.140
But--

00:16:44.140 --> 00:16:44.920
JOHN BOLTON: But not enough.

